  "statement": "The \\emph{intersection} of $A$ and $B$, denoted $A \\cap B$, is the set of all\nelements common to both:\n\\[\nA \\cap B \\;=\\; \\{\\, x \\mid x \\in A \\land x \\in B \\,\\}.\n\\]",
